item.description: Welcome to our latest roundup of what's going on in the indie game space. As a reminder, the latest edition of Steam Next Fest runs from February 23 until March 2, during which you'll be able to check out demos for hundreds of upcoming games. As it turns out, doing Tony Hawk Pro Skater-style tricks with a high-speed Japanese train absolutely rips.On Thursday, there were four showcases highlighting indie games all in a single day. item.description: Burger King has a new hotline that gives customers direct access to president Tom Curtis. In our Suspicion Economy, where everything’s a joke or a scam, BK is fighting cynicism with sincerity. And it just might work. I called Burger King president Tom Curtis a few times this week, but it went straight to voicemail. You can try too, his number is (305) 874-0520. ...
